{"id":28,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22563,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":28,"title":"“I Find No Fault in This Man”","subtitle":"","short_title":26,"uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/i-find-no-fault-in-this-man","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/i-find-no-fault-in-this-man.head1"},[".titleNumber","26"],["h1","“I Find No Fault in This Man”"]],[".bodyBlock",[".topic",["h2","Theme"],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/i-find-no-fault-in-this-man.p4"},"Nothing shows better the magnitude of the character of Jesus Christ than does the last day of his life, which is an example for all his disciples to follow."]],[".topic",["h2","Theme Analysis"],["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/i-find-no-fault-in-this-man.f1"},["ul.content-list alphaCaps",["li",["span.label","A."],["div",[".para","Jesus’ trial and crucifixion were illegal."]]],["li",["span.label","B."],["div",[".para","The final events of Jesus’ trial and crucifixion further attest to his divinity."]]],["li",["span.label","C."],["div",[".para","Jesus’ final statements and conduct show his love and concern for others."]]]]]],[".topic",["h2","Study Sources"],[".topic",["h3","New Testament Reading Assignment"],["div",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/i-find-no-fault-in-this-man.p11"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/26.36-46"},"Matthew 26:36-46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/14.32-42"},"Mark 14:32-42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.40-46"},"Luke 22:40-46"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/17.1-26"},"John 17:1-26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/18.1,2"